TITLE: Setting Unistyles Configuration
DESCRIPTION: How to apply all configuration options by calling the StyleSheet.configure function with themes, breakpoints, and settings.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jpudysz/react-native-unistyles/blob/main/docs/src/content/docs/v3/start/configuration.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import { StyleSheet } from 'react-native-unistyles'

StyleSheet.configure({
    themes: appThemes,
    breakpoints,
    settings
})
```

