TITLE: Configuring Settings in Unistyles
DESCRIPTION: Examples of different ways to configure Unistyles settings including specifying the initial theme with a string value, using a synchronous function, or enabling adaptive themes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jpudysz/react-native-unistyles/blob/main/docs/src/content/docs/v3/start/configuration.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
const settings = {
    initialTheme: 'light'
}

// or with a synchronous function
const settings = {
    initialTheme: () => {
        // get preferred theme from user's preferences/MMKV/SQL/StanJS etc.

        return storage.getString('preferredTheme') ?? 'light'
    }
}

// or with adaptive themes
const settings = {
    adaptiveThemes: true
}
```

