TITLE: Defining TypeScript Types for Unistyles
DESCRIPTION: How to override the library types for optimal TypeScript autocomplete and type safety for themes and breakpoints by extending the Unistyles interfaces.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jpudysz/react-native-unistyles/blob/main/docs/src/content/docs/v3/start/configuration.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
type AppThemes = typeof appThemes
type AppBreakpoints = typeof breakpoints

declare module 'react-native-unistyles' {
    export interface UnistylesThemes extends AppThemes {}
    export interface UnistylesBreakpoints extends AppBreakpoints {}
}
```

