TITLE: Configuring Breakpoints in Unistyles
DESCRIPTION: Example of defining responsive breakpoints in Unistyles. At least one breakpoint with value 0 is required to simulate the cascading behavior of CSS media queries.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jpudysz/react-native-unistyles/blob/main/docs/src/content/docs/v3/start/configuration.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
const breakpoints = {
    xs: 0, // <-- make sure to register one breakpoint with value 0
    sm: 300,
    md: 500,
    lg: 800,
    xl: 1200
    // use as many breakpoints as you need
}
```

