TITLE: Theme-Only Subscription with useUnistyles
DESCRIPTION: Example showing how to subscribe only to theme changes using the useUnistyles hook.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jpudysz/react-native-unistyles/blob/main/docs/src/content/docs/v3/references/use-unistyles.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
// subscribes to theme changes, rt is not yet used
const { theme, rt } = useUnistyles()
```

