TITLE: Creating Theme-Aware Dynamic Styles in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Example of defining styles that depend on the current theme in Unistyles. The container style uses theme colors for its background.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jpudysz/react-native-unistyles/blob/main/docs/src/content/docs/v3/references/web-styles.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_2

