TITLE: Registering Themes with StyleSheet.configure
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to register themes using the StyleSheet.configure method. Themes are registered using a unique name identifier that can be referenced later.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jpudysz/react-native-unistyles/blob/main/docs/src/content/docs/v3/guides/theming.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_2

