TITLE: Configuring Unistyles Babel Plugin in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: A comprehensive example of how to configure the Unistyles Babel plugin in babel.config.js with various options including autoProcessRoot, autoProcessImports, autoProcessPaths, and debug flag.
